snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda : Time Lost Official Trailer *Patch in Description* (Updated 08/15/24)
snippet.description:
Shout out to Cody Rhodes.

*Current Patch Version 1.02

Tested and Working on Retroarch Emulator (Mupen Core), Wii VC, Dolphin Emulator, Project 64 3.0.1

*Wii VC and Dolphin SAVE OFTEN* 

*Dolphin Emulator Config Guide - https://bthl.es/8L

*Nintendo 64 console untested, I *HIGHLY* recommend not using*

N64 .z64 Patch - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1fHYlsLFERqAjpGfBqk2QCGVjss-ERlNw/view?usp=sharing

Patch Over - "Legend of Zelda - Ocarina of Time (USA 1.0)"

WiiVC Patch - https://drive.google.com/file/d/13KiHY3DG8Jd2FV2wwOtieQOMHn5pjCG-/view?usp=sharing

Patch Over - "The Legend of Zelda - Ocarina of Time.wad"

Patch With Flips Patcher - https://www.romhacking.net/utilities/1040/

Join this discord - https://discord.gg/xMK5WuX5Bq
for Rom Hack discussion and news on my upcoming projects.
